images.name: Tua appreciates everyone's concerns about his health
images.caption: Dolphins quarterback Tua Tagovailoa addresses his injury history ahead of his return to practice this week.

articles.description: Tyreek Hill called Tua Tagovailoa's return to Dolphins practice Wednesday "beautiful." "Almost made me cry today like just having him in the lineup, having him call the plays, having him direct the offense, like just hearing his voice," the wideout said.
articles.headline: Tua Tagovailoa's practice return welcome sight for Dolphins
